  "detailed_description": "Smart Factory Tycoon is a tycoon management game about running your dream factory with robots. Design your dream factory, plan all steps of production, research new technologies and become a tycoon!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.poster.avif?t=1772897524\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.webm?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/32c3bc6efe1736ef0e0e2bd9e4593ba6.mp4?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Machines & Robots</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase new machinery and unlock advanced machines to produce every type of products in the market</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase new robots with varying colors and watch them coming to your factory by different transportation options: balloon, mine cart, boat, parachute, PWC or bus</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the skill points to level up your robots (Movement speed, processing speed, charge capacity, oil capacity)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase chargers, super chargers, wireless chargers, and lubricators for your robots rooms</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your machines, solar panels, wind turbines, chargers and lubricators for faster production and increased efficiency</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully automated machine-maintenance by drones</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.poster.avif?t=1772897524\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.webm?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/122986fd1e4bd3610a7718f22c30b2de.mp4?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Production & Market</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Plan all steps of the production</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase high quality raw material to produce healthy and durable products</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Analyze the market to be aware of trending products</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Check the general market categories (Basic-Medium-Master) and Special Orders</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Increase your health, durability and sustainability levels to be eligible for some products in the market</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.poster.avif?t=1772897524\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.webm?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/ed2324de73632ea2312551f447b0a343.mp4?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Sustainability & Economy</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase wind turbines and solar panels to reduce electricity costs and increase your sustainability</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Plant trees in your gardens to be a sustainable factory</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Earn more money and XP to take the first place in the leaderboard</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Do the math and be aware of your expenses! Don't go bankrupt!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.poster.avif?t=1772897524\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.webm?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/b3f04379a954d4174e5c5486dbfb597c.mp4?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Invest & Research & Development</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Research new technologies to improve your factory</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Purchase new buildings and deliver your products by rail, sea, and air</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build new rooms for robots and production</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Place your product zones and define their types as general or export</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Achieve milestones to earn more XP and level-up your factory</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.poster.avif?t=1772897524\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.webm?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810980/extras/49f70b692ba27234997ed95977282e71.mp4?t=1772897524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
